          acceptedAnswer: {
            '@type': 'Answer',
            text: 'IVF bypasses the reproductive system entirely by fertilizing eggs outside the body, while RRM identifies and treats the underlying condition preventing natural conception. RRM uses diagnostic tools like cycle charting, targeted bloodwork, and imaging to find the root cause, then applies medical or surgical treatment to restore function. Some patients pursue RRM before considering IVF; others use RRM alongside other treatments.',
          },
        },
